<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>마이클 키멜(Michael Kimmel)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/michael_kimmel_why_gender_equality_is_good_for_everyone_men_included?language=ko' lang='ko'>
양성 평등이 모두에게 유익한 이유 - 남자를 포함해서
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Sep 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Inspiring, Funny
